Package com.sympos2.models

Class Comentario

java.lang.Object
com.sympos2.models.Comentario
public class Comentario extends Object
This is the class to creates Comentario objects, which represents Comments and answers entities in database by the parameter: "tipo".

    • Comentario

      public Comentario(String id, String titulo, String texto, LocalDateTime fecha, int valoracion, String tipo, Long obra, String usuario)
      Constructor for the type "Comment"
      Parameters:
      id - String that collects the ObjectId of the comment in database
      titulo - String with the title of the comment
      texto - String with the text of the comment
      fecha - LocalDateTime with the moment of creation of the comment
      valoracion - int with the value of the work which the comment references
      tipo - String that represents the type of the Commentario, in this case probably will be "COMMENT"
      obra - Long with the Id of the Obra object which the comment references
      usuario - String with the id of the User which creates the comment

    • Comentario

      public Comentario(String id, String texto, LocalDateTime fecha, String tipo, Long obra, String usuario, String comment)
      /** Constructor for the type Answer
      Parameters:
      id - String that collects the ObjectId of the answer in database
      texto - String with the text of the answer
      fecha - LocalDateTime with the moment of creation of the answer
      tipo - String that represents the type of the Commentario, in this case probably will be "Answer"
      obra - Long with the Id of the Obra object which the comment references
      usuario - String with the id of the User which creates the answer
      comment - String with the id of the comment which answers
      valoracion - int with the value of the work which the answer references
